    "texts": [
        {
            "taxonTextType": "Previous names",
            "shortText": "<p><i>Plantago crassifolia </i>(Until recently confused with <i>P. crassifolia</i>, which is found in Europe and the Mediterranean coast of north Africa, but recent genetic evidence has shown that the South African species is distinct and the name <i>P. carnosa</i> has been resurrected as its correct name.)</p>",
            "shortTextKey": "taxon_text_9_9725",
            "longText": null,
            "longTextKey": null,
            "images": []
        },
        {
            "taxonTextType": "Identification features",
            "shortText": "<p>Short perennial forming a dense rosette of elongate, fleshy, lance-shaped light-green leaves, sometimes wooly in axils. Common along the margins of estuaries, lagoons or sheltered beaches. Upright stems reaching well above the leaves and each bear a spike of tiny white flowers.</p>",
            "shortTextKey": "taxon_text_1_9726",
            "longText": null,
            "longTextKey": null,
            "images": []
        },
        {
            "taxonTextType": "Adult size",
            "shortText": "<p>Typically reach a height of only about 20 cm. Leaves about 10-20 cm long.</p>",
            "shortTextKey": "taxon_text_2_9727",
            "longText": null,
            "longTextKey": null,
            "images": []
        },
        {
            "taxonTextType": "Distribution",
            "shortText": "<p><u>Global:</u> Endemic to South Africa,</p><p><u>Local/Regional:</u> In estuaries and salt-water lagoons extending from about Saldanha Bay to Eastern Cape.</p>",
            "shortTextKey": "taxon_text_3_9728",
            "longText": null,
            "longTextKey": null,
            "images": []
        },
        {
            "taxonTextType": "Biology",
            "shortText": "<p>Salt-tolerant plant that occurs low on sandy and muddy shores in both estuaries and fully-marine salt marshes ,<i>o</i>ften forming dense stands.</p>",
            "shortTextKey": "taxon_text_4_9729",
            "longText": null,
            "longTextKey": null,
            "images": []
        },
        {
            "taxonTextType": "Food / prey",
            "shortText": "<p>Photosynthetic.</p>",
            "shortTextKey": "taxon_text_5_9730",
            "longText": null,
            "longTextKey": null,
            "images": []
        },
        {
            "taxonTextType": "Reproduction",
            "shortText": "<p>Flower November to March. Wind pollinated.</p>",
            "shortTextKey": "taxon_text_6_9731",
            "longText": null,
            "longTextKey": null,
            "images": []
        },
        {
            "taxonTextType": "Similar species",
            "shortText": "<p>Distinctive and unlikely to be confused with other species.&nbsp;</p>",
            "shortTextKey": "taxon_text_7_9732",
            "longText": null,
            "longTextKey": null,
            "images": []
        }
    ],
